              adipisci veniam reiciendis laudantium voluptatem in incidunt! Quod
              doloribus nostrum autem! Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur
              adipisicing elit. Impedit adipisci veniam reiciendis laudantium
            </p>
            <div
              class="float-end mt-2 inline-flex transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
            >
              <img
                id="editButton1"
                src="edit-light.svg"
                class="editButtons z-20 mx-2 rounded-xl border-4 border-quaternaryTheme p-1 shadow-md shadow-tertiaryTheme ~h-[2.5rem]/[4rem] ~w-[2.5rem]/[4rem] hover:cursor-pointer active:scale-95 active:shadow-inner"
              />
              <label class="z-20 rounded-xl" for="confirmationModalToggle">
                <img
                  id="deleteButton1"
                  src="delete-light.svg"
                  class="deleteButtons z-20 rounded-xl border-4 border-quaternaryTheme p-2 shadow-md shadow-tertiaryTheme ~h-[2.5rem]/[4rem] ~w-[2.5rem]/[4rem] hover:cursor-pointer active:scale-95 active:shadow-inner"
                />
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- / accordion heading 1 -->
      </div>
      <!-- confirmation modal toggle -->
      <input type="checkbox" id="confirmationModalToggle" class="peer hidden" />
      <!-- modal backdrop/wrapper -->
      <label
        for="confirmationModalToggle"
        class="fixed inset-0 z-30 hidden bg-black bg-opacity-50 peer-checked:block"
      ></label>
      <!-- modal gradient background -->
      <div
        id="confirmationModalBackground"
        class="animate__animated animate__zoomIn fixed inset-y-2/4 z-30 hidden w-fit self-center rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-secondaryTheme via-tertiaryTheme to-quaternaryTheme p-2 shadow-lg shadow-tertiaryTheme peer-checked:block"
      >
        <div
          id="confirmationModalBox"
          class="z-30 flex h-fit flex-col rounded-2xl bg-secondaryTheme ~w-[25rem]/[50rem]"
        >
          <h1
            class="josefin-sans-importFont self-center p-3 text-center font-extrabold text-tertiaryTheme ~text-xl/5xl"
          >
            Are you sure you want to delete this review?
          </h1>
          <div
            class="josefin-sans-importFont flex flex-grow items-center justify-evenly p-3 ~text-base/3xl"
          >
            <label
              for="confirmationModalToggle"
              id="closeConfirmationModal"
              class="mx-2 rounded-xl border-4 border-secondaryTheme bg-tertiaryTheme text-center font-semibold text-secondaryTheme shadow-md shadow-tertiaryTheme ~w-[7.5rem]/[15rem] ~py-1/3 hover:cursor-pointer hover:bg-gradient-to-br active:scale-95 active:shadow-inner"
            >
              Close
            </label>
            <button
              class="mx-2 rounded-xl border-4 border-secondaryTheme bg-tertiaryTheme font-semibold text-secondaryTheme shadow-md shadow-tertiaryTheme ~w-[7.5rem]/[15rem] ~py-1/3 hover:bg-gradient-to-r active:scale-95 active:shadow-inner"
            >
              Delete!
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- / confirmation modal -->
    </div>

    <script src="/notes-bundle.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
